OL,3,CLorry driver caught eating bowl of
OL,4,Ccereal at the wheel
OL,6,FNational Highways has released footage
OL,7,Fof incidents of bad driving, including
OL,8,Fa man using a laptop and another
OL,9,Fwithout a seatbelt
OL,11,FA motorist eating a bowl of cereal at
OL,12,Fthe wheel and another typing on a
OL,13,Flaptop while driving a lorry have been
OL,14,Fcaught in a police crackdown.
OL,16,FOfficers using an unmarked lorry
OL,17,Ffilmed the trucker enjoying his
OL,18,Fbreakfast while driving in North
OL,19,FYorkshire.
