OL,3,CLorry driver caught eating bowl of
OL,4,Ccereal at the wheel
OL,6,FThe man using his laptop was caught on
OL,7,Fcamera in South Yorkshire, where the
OL,8,Fdriver of a Ford Focus was seen using
OL,9,Fboth hands to text on a mobile phone.
OL,11,FSeveral other drivers were filmed
OL,12,Fwithout their seatbelts fastened.
OL,14,FThe incidents were spotted during
OL,15,FOperation Tramline, an initiative to
OL,16,Fcombat poor driving, on the A1, M1 and
OL,17,FM18 during November and December.
OL,19,FThe operation sees police use an
OL,20,Funmarked HGV cab to patrol the roads
OL,21,Ffrom an elevated position.
