OL,3,CLorry driver caught eating bowl of
OL,4,Ccereal at the wheel
OL,6,FOfficers from North Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Ffound one driver tucking into his
OL,8,Fbreakfast bowl at the wheel while an
OL,9,FHGV driver stuck his middle finger up
OL,10,Fwhen it dawned on him he had been
OL,11,Fspotted wearing no seatbelt.
OL,13,FMore than 190 offences were recorded
OL,14,Fby five forces in North Yorkshire,
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire, West Yorkshire,
OL,16,FNorthumbria and Durham between 4
OL,17,FNovember and 13 December.
