OL,6,FNicola Clayton, of National Highways,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The HGV cabs are an important
OL,8,Fpart of our commitment to tackling
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and those who take
OL,10,Funnecessary risks with their own
OL,11,Fsafety and that of the majority of
OL,12,Fdrivers who respect the rules of the
OL,13,Froad.
OL,15,F"The number of people found not
OL,16,Fwearing their seatbelt or using their
OL,17,Fmobile phone and other devices while
OL,18,Fdriving is quite alarming."
