OL,6,FInsp Clive Turner, of North Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "It is always
OL,8,Fdisappointing to find so many drivers
OL,9,Fwho are prepared to put their life and
OL,10,Fothers lives at risk for the sake of
OL,11,Fnot wearing a seat belt or checking
OL,12,Ftheir mobile phones."
